{"tid":453754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲傭將女僱主的自慰器放到2歲女童下體","createTime":"2017-10-31T13:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T09:57:49.000Z","uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"530b1abea3b3ae51fa470ac7d4b15173c7611368","tid":453754,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:00:31.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=aDAjh%2BXfj1h18Xwx2p8ORv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=90053f18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】38歲菲律賓藉女傭Gina Canuu BUDUAN今(31日)在觀塘法院被控一項虐兒罪，指她涉於今年10月，在將軍澳一私人屋苑單位內，虐待2歲女童。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方案情透露，被告涉將女僱主的自慰器放到女童下體，女僱主其後發現女童下體紅腫揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告今日暫時毋須答辯，控方申請將案件押後12月13日再訊，期間索取女童醫療報告及諮詢法律意見，被告須還押。<br />\n<br />\n【更多即時新聞詳情請上東網新聞】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B6%89%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%AA%E6%85%B0%E5%99%A8%E8%99%902%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%BB-%E8%8F%B2%E5%82%AD%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%AF%A9-083602707.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2585%25B0%25E5%2599%25A8%25E8%2599%25902%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E8%258F%25B2%25E5%2582%25AD%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%25AF%25A9-083602707.html&d=aDAjh%2BXfj1h18Xwx2p8ORv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d60c00be\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B6%89%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%AA%E6%85%B0%E5%99%A8%E8%99%902%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%BB-%E8%8F%B2%E5%82%AD%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%AF%A9-083602707.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6dd9c3c802d2b013c8d36a50e5fe99c84b5811","tid":453754,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96673d4